title: U of M $850 includes utilities
posting_body: ['Nice large  one bedroom in secured QUIET building, new windows, large eat in kitchen, beautiful built in bookshelves in living room and 10 feet ceilings.', ' Many windows.', 'Apartment faces the south side, so lots of natural sunshine 🌞', 'Excellent location, close to U of M, North Central College, MCTC, Hennepin county medical center, coffee shops, bakeries, Aldi grocery store,  on several bus lines, street parking,  easy access to 94 and 35 W, walk to downtown Minneapolis.', 'Our building is a quiet community of students and professionals, ample bicycle storage, full laundry room with coin operated washers and dryers.', ' Best deal in Minneapolis, $850.00', 'ALL utilities included and complimentary  WiFi.', ' **Requires a security deposit of $850', 'Rental history and criminal background check required', 'Must have no Felonies or Evictions', 'No smoking', '200.00 non refundable cat fee', 'NO dogs', 'Available Mid August.', 'Tenant is willing to move out early.', '12 month lease', 'I don’t respond to e mails.', 'Please call for more information or to schedule a private showing,', 'show contact info', '.']
